text: Maybank Chinatown, please remove your number if there is no intention to take calls. Been calling even the 1800 number, no one will pick up. They pick up n drop the call. Have to listen to the prerecorded message and then the phone will ring and thats 4-5 min of your time wasted. Terrible. They prefer customer visit the branches.

Friendly staff but always super busy.

Get your queue no before heading down...

The male officer at counter 5 (didn't get his name) on 13 Aug 24 between 12.30 to 12.40pm, is courteous and fast in handling my renewal of FD.  When I took out my passbook, he even offered to update for me before I asked for it. All done within 10 minutes. Keep up the good work!

The warm and friendly service from Shufen at reception and the efficiency of Christine at the counter was amazing. This branch gets really busy at peak hour but I have never had delays in getting my requests processed. The team here are very helpful and detailed in making sure I understand how to login or troubleshoot online banking matters.
Extreme Long waiting. Customers complaining, queue started moving faster.
